{"tid":2122153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Huawei 鏡頭並非 LEICA 在德國製造","createTime":"2020-07-23T21:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:28:35.000Z","uid":26770,"like":280,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"78b10a4d5c3a2b0cc2fd4c9e4b502e6ef4917425","tid":2122153,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:51:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/04/20/huawei-p9-leica-camera-is-made-by-other-manufacturer/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F04%2F20%2Fhuawei-p9-leica-camera-is-made-by-other-manufacturer%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6AexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=aad85a1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/04/20/huawei-p9-leica-camera-is-made-by-other-manufacturer/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\nHuawei 近年積極擴展手機業務，如今成績已有目共睹，並成為了中國最大的手機廠商。與此同時，Huawei 月初發表的新旗艦機 P9 及 P9 Plus 更獲得不少人注意，皆因該兩款新機採用了 LEICA 出品的雙鏡頭。不過正當大家以為該鏡頭是於德國製造，原來實情卻並非如此。<br />\n<br />\n作為全球知名的相機生產商，LEICA 相機質素之高一向都是眾所周知，而且德國製造這點更予人信心保證，所以 Huawei 今次成功與 LEICA 合作，外界當然有極大期望。不過雙方今次合作卻同時帶來一個疑問，因為 LEICA 本身並沒有手機鏡頭的生產線，而 Huawei 亦沒有生產這款組件，那麼 P9 及 P9 Plus 所採用的 Summarit H 1:2.2/27 ASPH 鏡頭到底又是如何生產呢？<br />\n<br />\n最近有人就針對這個問題尋找答案，最後就發現該款鏡頭原來確實並非 LEICA 在德國製造，反而他們授權國內一間名為舜宇（Sunny Optical）的手機鏡頭模組廠商代工生產。留意 P9 鏡頭是由 LEICA 負責設計、授權及驗收，至於 CMOS 感光元件及鏡頭的組裝則是出自舜宇之手。雖然由 LEICA 授權及掛上自己的品牌，質素至於應該有一定保證，不過如今變成了中國製造，相信大家聽到之後信心應該會大打折扣吧？"},{"pid":"a94add71eca88bcb475a5df57298f13e11c829e7","tid":2122153,"uid":70487,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:52:01.000Z","msg":"唯一優點都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2831355c4f694bb519a4981b35a71af752cc4a0d","tid":2122153,"uid":22054,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:52:36.000Z","msg":"LEICA都貼牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd2767862dd23f1e562d6769c7b51431bb21135","tid":2122153,"uid":126731,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:56:02.000Z","msg":"賣貼紙係奶衈副業黎。"},{"pid":"511eed7282ab4c051a45acabb7b2f98e7c1cf17b","tid":2122153,"uid":26770,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:56:33.000Z","msg":"華為公司標榜的哈曼調音/與Devialet 的合作係同一回事<br />\n<br />\n呢堆超級品牌就收授權費比華為用自己個名去吸客<br />\n呢個就係人權大國點解唔就中國人權問題出聲的原因(國內龍頭企業咬緊赤共綜援)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">而更重要的係消費者以為平價買到超級品牌, 實際係假象</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">而香港消委會完全扮盲唔出聲<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"602ccade3b7d6b4475fc84daa133e6947bd53e9f","tid":2122153,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:57:14.000Z","msg":"係唔係仲出個蔡司鏡？<br />\n咁睇嚟應該都唔係德國做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269cb5175c57635d008bffc58398ca2c61516ef2","tid":2122153,"uid":126731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"602ccade3b7d6b4475fc84daa133e6947bd53e9f","tid":2122153,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:57:14.000Z","msg":"係唔係仲出個蔡司鏡？<br />\n咁睇嚟應該都唔係德國做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:59:43.000Z","msg":"呢個係sony 相機"},{"pid":"ce33d75cb8d44b7641abda0a66e0046002aecdbf","tid":2122153,"uid":26770,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"602ccade3b7d6b4475fc84daa133e6947bd53e9f","tid":2122153,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:57:14.000Z","msg":"係唔係仲出個蔡司鏡？<br />\n咁睇嚟應該都唔係德國做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:00:41.000Z","msg":"CHANNEL同CHANEL的分別<br />\n其實同淘佬堆超平品牌野一樣<br />\n可以差到連個盒都抄得唔似<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為精在比錢買貼紙呃人,再賣更高價<br />\n咪就係東門經營手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ab737fe663ffa93a4fef3ea6ab91b38bfa897c","tid":2122153,"uid":48631,"like":19